605
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,700
C'est quoi ce bordel maintenant ?

606
00:40:11,600 --> 00:40:12,600
<i>Extraordinaire !</i>

607
00:40:12,700 --> 00:40:14,684
La maman de Butchie
